@startuml Admin_Bulk_Actions
title Admin Bulk Actions Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Admin Controller" as Ctrl
database "Database" as DB
participant "Security Log" as Log

Admin -> FE: Select Users & Choose Action\n(Verify/Unverify/Delete)
FE -> API: POST /admin/bulk-action
note right of FE: {userIds: [...], action: "..."}

API -> Ctrl: Handle Bulk Request
Ctrl -> DB: updateMany({_id: {$in: userIds}}, updates)
activate DB
DB --> Ctrl: Success (n Modified)
deactivate DB

Ctrl -> Log: Log "bulk_action_{type}" with count
Ctrl --> API: 200 OK {modifiedCount: n}
API --> FE: Show Success Toast

@enduml
